It's like

00:20:49.280 --> 00:20:51.370
someone formidably strong

00:20:51.850 --> 00:20:54.240
threw several blades at Song Jingye at the same time

00:20:54.570 --> 00:20:56.170
and cut him into pieces easily.

00:21:00.330 --> 00:21:00.930
I see.

