Then, he pushed the lion down from above

00:21:39.720 --> 00:21:40.930
to drive the tussah silk

00:21:41.370 --> 00:21:42.240
to Song Jingye, right?

00:21:43.410 --> 00:21:44.000
Right.

00:21:45.440 --> 00:21:46.040
Young Mistress.

