It corresponds to the four grooves upstairs.

00:23:01.890 --> 00:23:03.890
In that case, a healthy man

00:23:04.130 --> 00:23:05.960
can move the stone lion easily.

00:23:06.480 --> 00:23:07.480
Not to mention

00:23:07.480 --> 00:23:09.000
a master with great internal power.

00:23:10.850 --> 00:23:11.650
Where are the balls?

00:23:12.170 --> 00:23:13.970
They must have been smashed when it fell.

00:23:14.120 --> 00:23:15.730
How do you know that?

00:23:18.280 --> 00:23:19.850
It's easy.

00:23:19.850 --> 00:23:21.250
It's the same as treating a patient.

00:23:22.120 --> 00:23:24.090
It's about observation, auscultation and olfaction, inquiry, and palpation.

