After we entered the Lin's Mansion,

00:23:26.730 --> 00:23:28.280
we found that the two stone lions

00:23:28.280 --> 00:23:29.370
were placed wrongly.

00:23:29.530 --> 00:23:31.960
I knew there was something wrong with it.

00:23:32.090 --> 00:23:32.890
This is "observation".

00:23:33.840 --> 00:23:35.210
Then, we entered the building.

00:23:35.370 --> 00:23:37.090
I smelled blood on the beam.

00:23:37.090 --> 00:23:38.120
So, I deduced

00:23:38.680 --> 00:23:40.840
that Song Jingye died nearby,

00:23:41.440 --> 00:23:42.440
and

00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:44.200
he was cut into pieces in the air.

00:23:44.850 --> 00:23:45.910
This is "auscultation and olfaction".

