00:35:40.530 --> 00:35:41.530
most of the people in our organization

00:35:41.930 --> 00:35:43.650
who were involved in this

00:35:44.530 --> 00:35:45.840
were killed.

00:35:46.160 --> 00:35:47.530
I was afraid of being killed.

00:35:48.530 --> 00:35:49.490
So, I found a way

00:35:50.160 --> 00:35:51.280
to escape from the Breakwall.

00:35:51.930 --> 00:35:52.970
I used a painting

00:35:54.130 --> 00:35:55.160
to fake my death to escape.

00:35:55.800 --> 00:35:56.880
Does Song Jingye's death

00:35:57.450 --> 00:35:58.800
have anything to do with you?

00:36:03.650 --> 00:36:04.800
Kind of.

00:36:05.880 --> 00:36:06.490
But

00:36:07.360 --> 00:36:08.880
I just gave the murderer

